# Rykard, Lord of Blasphemy · the praetor who fed himself to the serpent

Rykard was praetor of the Volcano Manor, a son of Radagon and Rennala. In defiance of the Erdtree he fed himself to the God-Devouring Serpent of Mt. Gelmir, becoming one with it, so that his blasphemy might swallow the very gods.

The manor he ruled still serves him. Its recusants hunt Tarnished in his name, and his great blade — the Blasphemous Blade — drinks life. What began as a family's ambition turned, in him, literally all-consuming.

His emergence is natural: not the storm, not the unseen, not grace — but flesh joined to beast, fire-as-fire on the mountain of Gelmir, a body made one with the serpent and the burning land itself.
